Knickity-knock!

250
00:16:29.640 --> 00:16:30.600
(WHISTLING)

251
00:16:30.680 --> 00:16:32.600
Watch your angle there.

252
00:16:33.320 --> 00:16:35.120
(CONTINUES WHISTLING)

253
00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:57.120
TERENCE: (SOFTLY) Knock-knock!
Who's there?

254
00:16:57.360 --> 00:17:00.480
Knock. Knock who?
Knock-knock-knickity-knock!

255
00:17:01.200 --> 00:17:02.240
Knickity-knock.

256
00:17:02.520 --> 00:17:03.920
(SQUEAKING)

257
00:17:12.440 --> 00:17:13.760
(GLASS SHATTERING)

258
00:17:33.920 --> 00:17:35.120
Steady.

259
00:17:35.880 --> 00:17:38.720
You gotta be easy.
This is the tricky part.

260
00:17:39.720 --> 00:17:40.920
I know.

261
00:17:42.880 --> 00:17:45.440
All right, now we gotta match
the trajectory of the light beam

262
00:17:45.520 --> 00:17:47.520
-with the...
-Got it. Thanks.

263
00:17:47.600 --> 00:17:49.160
-With the...
-Okay. Yeah, I know.

264
00:17:49.240 --> 00:17:50.560
-With the...
-Shh!

265
00:17:53.080 --> 00:17:56.360
-The curvature of the moonstone.
-Will you please...

266
00:18:03.400 --> 00:18:04.680
(GROANS)

267
00:18:05.160 --> 00:18:09.240
Tink, it looks like you need
some sort of, you know, sharp thingy.

268
00:18:10.400 --> 00:18:12.480
That's exactly what I need.

269
00:18:12.600 --> 00:18:15.400
Could you go out
and find me something sharp?

270
00:18:15.480 --> 00:18:17.760
You got it. I'll be right back.

271
00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:19.480
Take your time.

272
00:18:20.320 --> 00:18:21.880
(CLANK HUMMING)

273
00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:29.920
Clank, what is that?

274
00:18:30.800 --> 00:18:35.200
